  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "33d6a52637f824f012c959993d2bcbf3a18cc2506f0c7d812d6405b2df9973dc": "Welcome back, [?]. How are those repairs going?",
    "3a43907dea18c73468d3192641d1ff191c8cc4efff55106c728cc595deddee39": "You're back, [?]! What news from the Pearl?",
    "468a086b0a34d750cbd12ce1906b37605345b36640b95910c3bb7d5160671e7c": "Welcome back, [?]. Any luck with that gryphon?",
    "5cd6b0d4f355600770b235d9de2dd41480843efd69cd37bacd3d9b5fc3f3409a": "Hurry, [?]! You need to head to the Little Pearl!",
    "8adaca88b84b0c183b4adf6c7ebe7594b380b87204215780f4142e6caf21ee23": "More than that! You need more rest as well. [?], we should give her the time she needs. Return to us later once she has rested.",
    "a119a9ba12490a931ff8446ea14271c8cfd3ec176cd10773c269a33b2bc6a98b": "I wouldn't say no to a bit of extra help, though Floopa is right, [?]. Do not feel like you need to do any more.",
    "bd0a6abb45950bdd656079031991eae23b8c4987623870089e5aedc665d0f532": "Oh, [?], I hope you haven't taken offense! It's really nothing personal. It's just how we do things.",
    "f34be92e9989373d965f834d7593cdba642914f86304e61ed45794fb0579f7e5": "No, no, no! Thank you, [?]! We will talk again soon."
  }
